A simple bash script created from the information on: http://code.google.com/p/smali/wiki/DeodexInstructions. This script is used to deodex Android files in the /system/app or /system/framework folder.

Put script in 'system/' dir of firmware and run, i use baksmali-1.4.2.jar and mali-1.4.2.jar from https://code.google.com/p/smali/downloads/list

Tested on: Ubuntu 12.04 64bit
